PrecisLeasing to The Montreal Centre for Technological Initiative (a non-profit organization), for a term of sixty-five years, of some 29.5 hectares of unserviced vacant land situate at Montreal International Airport, in the City of Dorval, Quebec, which are to be used for the development of a research and high-technology industrial park.
